1
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:19,120
Yan Ge,

2
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:20,280
what are you...

3
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:23,000
Sister Su,

4
00:00:24,359 --> 00:00:25,280
you were right.

5
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,960
I shouldn't have stayed here in the first place.

6
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:29,839
When I'm not around,

7
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:31,280
please take care of yourself.

8
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,759
Don't let the corruption harm you.

9
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:35,439
If the Women's Clinic can continue,

10
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:39,520
it will be a blessing for all the ladies.

11
00:00:50,799 --> 00:00:52,000
You just left.

12
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,359
Have you ever asked me?

13
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:57,679
Didn't we agree

14
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:00,960
to break free from the shackles of society?

15
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,799
She said

16
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,959
she didn't want to harm the Women's Clinic.

17
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:15,000
If the clinic falls

18
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:15,640
because of rumors,

19
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,519
wouldn't it just satisfy

20
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,719
those who spread malicious gossip?

21
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,480
Do you

22
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,000
want them to succeed?

23
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,799
These rumors have nothing to do with you.

24
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,760
There's no smoke without fire.

25
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:37,280
You've been in the Women's Clinic for a long time.

26
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,120
Now these rumors suddenly come out.

27
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,200
Someone must be

28
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:44,079
using your identity to do this.

29
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:45,959
The world is so big.

30
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:47,640
There are storms everywhere.

31
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,599
With friends to share the storm,

32
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:51,640
with friends.

33
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,159
Yan Ge,

34
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,519
the Women's clinic

35
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:55,920
needs you.

36
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,400
Yes.

37
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,960
I thought you were dead.

38
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:31,400
I didn't expect her to be alive.

39
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,840
I trained you for so many years.

40
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:38,159
I feel so sorry for you.

41
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:39,719
Do you know

42
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,960
how much money I lost because of you?

43
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,560
How dare you collude with outsiders to deceive me?

44
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:49,560
I advise you to behave yourself.

45
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:52,039
You assisted Shen Yuan in committing treason,

46
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,120
stealing tax silver,

47
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:54,400
and disrupting the order of the mutual market.

48
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:56,159
You're already hard to escape from the same responsibility.

49
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,919
If anything happens to me,

50
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,759
then it would be a greater crime.

51
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,520
Who are you to teach me?

52
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,280
Who do you think you are, a golden branch and jade leaf?

53
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,719
You're just a toy for others to play with,

54
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,439
in a brothel.

55
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:19,800
Even if you disappear,

56
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:23,879
who would stand up for you?

57
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:24,759
Stop!

58
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:28,800
I...

59
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:30,919
I'll stand up for her!

60
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:32,560
Sijun,

61
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,639
you must leave!

62
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:39,879
Leave now!

63
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,639
They don't care about consequences

64
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,199
They won't go easy on you.

65
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,240
Just go!

66
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,719
I'm not leaving.

67
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,520
If I leave,

68
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:51,360
who will stand up for you?

69
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,840
A poor boy dares to ruin my business?

70
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,000
Beat him!

71
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:57,919
Yes!

72
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:00,919
Stop!

73
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,400
Take it out on me!

74
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,560
Sijingting!

75
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,080
Sijingting!

76
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:06,960
Sijingting!

77
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,520
Stop!

78
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:11,520
Stop!

79
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:13,840
Stop!

80
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,439
Let go of me!

81
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,680
Stop!

82
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,399
Sijingting!

83
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,639
Sijingting!

84
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,720
Stop!

85
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,600
Where's the madam?

86
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:32,720
Where is she?

87
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:34,839
Watch them.

88
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,000
Follow me.

89
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:37,519
My lord,

90
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,000
what's going on?

91
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:42,560
Everyone, stay here and wait for questioning.

92
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,399
No one is allowed to leave.

93
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:45,720
Those who disobey

94
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:47,600
will be treated as accomplices.

95
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,319
This is the Bright Moon Pavilion,

96
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,360
not somewhere you can just make up rules!

97
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,319
Don't you know who's backing me?

98
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,399
The Supreme Court is here by imperial decree.

99
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,720
Tell us,

100
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:01,120
who exactly is backing you?

101
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:04,040
We'll investigate together.

102
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,439
The Prime Minister's Pavilion?

103
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,120
Yan Ge,

104
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,000
I'll untie you.

105
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:16,160
The...

106
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,399
The Supreme Court?

107
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:21,480
Are you here to investigate Shen Yuan's trade?

108
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:23,480
The case involves tax silver,

109
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,759
and the West Market Magistrate is involved in a murder.

110
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:28,240
It's naturally transferred to the Supreme Court.

111
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:30,480
You covered up

112
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:32,399
Shen Yuan and Su Erman's crimes.

113
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,199
You'll be treated as a criminal.

114
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,360
I don't understand what you're talking about.

115
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:38,920
Guards,

116
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,480
Take her away.

117
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:40,680
Wait.

118
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,519
Wait.

119
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,639
I'm willing to tell you everything I know.

120
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,399
Can I remain anonymous?

121
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,439
As long as you spare my life,

122
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,600
I can tell you anything.

123
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,439
I have evidence.

124
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,199
I'll go get it right now.

125
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,519
I'll go get it right away.

126
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:55,560
Seal off the front and back doors.

127
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,199
Are you okay?

128
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,399
I'm fine.

129
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:08,680
Go!

130
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,279
What's that noise?

131
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,519
Go after them!

132
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,480
Xuezhi,

133
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,160
these are all your favorites.

134
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,600
Sesame cakes,

135
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:08,720
ancient pastries,

136
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,279
and through-the-flower cakes.

137
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,600
All freshly heated.

138
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,600
[I killed your mother.]

139
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,000
[I've avenged you.]

140
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,720
[You can rest in peace]

141
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,839
[in the afterlife.]

142
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,439
[Don't be a dancer in the next life.]

143
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,439
[Don't have]

144
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,720
[a sister like me.]

145
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,319
[If there's a next life,]

146
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,839
[I hope you are born in a scholarly family,]

147
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,319
[reading by the window,]

148
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,439
[enjoying flowers in the yard,]

149
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,199
[and live a peaceful life.]

150
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,199
I found this at the door.

151
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,000
Yin,

152
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,920
is this letter

153
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,000
true?

154
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:33,320
It was written by A'Lang himself.

155
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,960
Everything in it is true.

156
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,879
What if

157
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,360
I don't believe you?

158
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,279
It's you, Mr. Xiao.

159
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,639
You found me.

160
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,960
If you don't believe me,

161
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,559
I'll just leave.

162
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,039
Stop!

163
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,639
Tell me more.

164
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,720
Previously, Xiao

165
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,840
learned about the trade

166
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,679
through the tax silver case.

167
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,039
He plans to get close to you

168
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,639
to investigate the accounts

169
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,279
of our family's dealings with the Saro.

170
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,600
Though we have

171
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,919
[have had a long-standing grudge,]

172
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,240
[but we]

173
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,679
[still maintain our integrity.]

174
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:13,480
[This wasn't my choice.]

175
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,120
[It's just that what Xiao is investigating]

176
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,919
[involves too many parties.]

177
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,960
Since he's so determined to investigate this,

178
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,759
let's help him out.

179
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,840
Take him to Panyu.

180
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,080
Send this letter to Panyu immediately.

181
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,679
[But who would have thought that this trip]

182
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:28,919
[would be a farewell forever.]

183
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,320
Halt!

184
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,960
[A'Lang intended to set up a trap in Panyu,]

185
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,240
[but was suddenly attacked by bandits.]

186
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,519
[Under the barrage of arrows,]

187
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,039
[the caravan was wiped out.]

188
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,159
[We were pushed to the edge of a cliff]

189
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:39,080
[by the bandits and had nowhere to escape.]

190
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,320
[I pretended to be dead to survive.]

191
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:43,399
A'Lang!

192
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,159
A'Lang!

193
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:48,200
What should we do now?

194
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:50,600
The young lady is waiting for you.

195
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,279
[That day,]

196
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,039
[I was the only one who survived.]

197
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,720
[Why did Yin Shifeng]

198
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,840
[do this to me?]

199
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,840
Su Erman didn't keep his word.

200
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,799
He didn't pay us

201
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,399
for several shipments.

202
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,919
Labor, materials,

203
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:07,759
passage tax,

204
00:10:07,759 --> 00:10:09,440
dock fees,

205
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,639
and various other expenses.

206
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:11,960
As merchants,

207
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:14,360
we don't always have cash on hand.

208
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,080
A'Lang has been covering

209
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,360
the costs for several shipments,

210
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,440
leaving us with significant debts.

211
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,919
Yin,

212
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:23,759
we still can't

213
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:25,360
the Saro Trading Firm

214
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,960
is still unable to repay.

215
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,279
I hope you

216
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,320
can extend us some more time.

217
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:31,440
Extend more time?

218
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,559
My family has been in business for three generations

219
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,600
and has never been late on a single tax payment.

220
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,879
The money I've fronted for you

221
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,120
has already exceeded a hundred thousand taels.

222
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:39,919
The wharf,

223
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,720
tariffs,

224
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:41,600
and labor

225
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,159
are all on me.

226
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:45,000
You want to

227
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,639
back out?

228
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,720
Yin,

229
00:10:49,679 --> 00:10:51,679
don't say that.

230
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,039
Rest assured,

231
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:56,240
the spice transport for Panyu

232
00:10:56,639 --> 00:10:58,320
is yours.

233
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,399
As for the money you're owed,

234
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,600
just make up for it in the market.

235
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:05,559
This time,

236
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,600
30% of the revenue

237
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:08,919
from the market

238
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,039
will go to you.

239
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:13,399
That should cover your previous losses.

240
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:15,320
As long as

241
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:18,039
you bring Xiao Tingzhu to Panyu this time.

242
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,919
He's just a merchant.

243
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,200
He shouldn't have gotten involved

244
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,279
the investigation of the Ministry of Revenue.

245
00:11:23,519 --> 00:11:24,759
If he's smart,

246
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:25,919
he'll keep his mouth shut.

247
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,480
If not,

248
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,240
I'll make him shut up.

249
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,360
Then why

250
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:37,240
did my father want me to marry Yin Xinyue?

251
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:39,480
The reason

252
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:42,399
your father could return to Chang'an

253
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:46,399
was entirely due to your heroic rescue.

254
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:47,720
That day,

255
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,480
he could have escaped.

256
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:49,759
Quick!

257
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:50,360
Go!

258
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,879
But he turned back to save your father,

259
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,440
blocked three sword strikes for him,

260
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:54,879
and gave him a chance to escape.

261
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:57,519
But what Xiao didn't know was

262
00:11:57,759 --> 00:11:58,600
that all of this

263
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:01,320
was part of your plan.

264
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:02,200
But

265
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,320
he also

266
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,559
got himself killed.

267
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:07,320
If that's the case,

268
00:12:07,799 --> 00:12:08,960
why did he go back to save my father?

269
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,879
Because of you.

270
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,919
You are his only weakness.

271
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,919
Even if he returns to Chang'an,

272
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:18,360
he will be burdened with debts.

273
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,080
But if he saves Xiao,

274
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,000
he can marry you

275
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,360
[and marry you]

276
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,759
[as his savior.]

277
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:27,240
[That's how]

278
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:29,799
[he protects you.]

279
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,240
Good.

280
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:36,600
Good.

281
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:37,679
Good.

282
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,879
He's calculated everything,

283
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:42,679
even risking

284
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,799
his own life

285
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:49,120
for his daughter's future.

286
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:54,960
What a loving father.

287
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,120
My lord.

288
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:57,600
Nong,

289
00:12:58,879 --> 00:12:59,879
you must not reveal

290
00:13:00,519 --> 00:13:02,679
a word of today's events to anyone.

291
00:13:02,759 --> 00:13:03,399
Yes.

292
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:04,320
See the guest out.

293
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,559
Greetings, my lady.

294
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,159
Lady Yin, you're here.

295
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,440
Please, have a seat.

296
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,559
Why didn't you go to the clinic today?

297
00:13:21,559 --> 00:13:23,440
Did you come to greet me?

298
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,360
My lady,

299
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,519
please forgive me.

300
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,919
My clinic has been very busy these days.

301
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:29,759
I've been

302
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:31,799
worried about your old illness,

303
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,159
so I specially sought out some ancient remedies

304
00:13:36,519 --> 00:13:37,799
and brought them to you.

305
00:13:40,399 --> 00:13:41,840
That's very thoughtful of you.

306
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,120
Yunzhou,

307
00:13:43,879 --> 00:13:45,639
look at your future wife.

308
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,720
She cares for me far more than you do.

309
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:48,759
A chronic illness

310
00:13:48,879 --> 00:13:50,159
cannot be cured

311
00:13:50,519 --> 00:13:51,559
by just a few herbs.

312
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:54,279
This is not something to rush.

313
00:13:55,519 --> 00:13:57,440
If the root is harmed,

314
00:13:58,519 --> 00:13:59,919
it could cause great trouble.

315
00:14:01,639 --> 00:14:03,399
Some people lack medical knowledge,

316
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:06,120
relying only on their foolish devotion,

317
00:14:06,919 --> 00:14:10,120
which has led to your prolonged suffering.

318
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,600
The Art of Medicine

319
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:14,000
is all about treating the right symptoms

320
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,200
and balancing yin and yang.

321
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:18,240
I would never let medicine

322
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,799
harm your health.

323
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,240
This prescription

324
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,879
has been carefully considered.

325
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:25,200
It's all about gradual progress

326
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,879
and gentle treatment.

327
00:14:31,519 --> 00:14:32,879
What's going on with you two today?

328
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:35,279
Why are you two so hostile?

329
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,679
Your words are like daggers.

330
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,559
Madam, please don't take offense.

331
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:40,799
Madam,

332
00:14:41,159 --> 00:14:43,000
your condition

333
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,759
worries me the most.

334
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,919
How could I possibly argue

335
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:50,879
with Mr. Xiao over such trivial matters?

336
00:14:52,679 --> 00:14:54,159
It rained heavily last night,

337
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:56,879
and many of my herbs were ruined.

338
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,480
I'll excuse myself now.

339
00:15:00,559 --> 00:15:03,240
Hope you get well soon,

340
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,000
and you can be relieved,

341
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:09,039
and your family can live in peace.

342
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,080
That's for sure.

343
00:15:15,039 --> 00:15:16,559
Did you two have a fight?

344
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:17,799
It's okay.

345
00:15:19,799 --> 00:15:21,679
The mourning period is almost over.

346
00:15:22,279 --> 00:15:23,360
Your marriage

347
00:15:23,759 --> 00:15:25,799
will be on the agenda soon.

348
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:28,080
Why are you still acting like a child,

349
00:15:28,519 --> 00:15:30,120
quarreling with the young lady?

350
00:15:31,759 --> 00:15:32,360
About the marriage,

351
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,679
my father had already instructed

352
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:37,000
that it should be decided by Madam.

353
00:15:37,879 --> 00:15:40,480
I'll take my leave now.

354
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:41,200
Hmm.

355
00:15:47,519 --> 00:15:50,000
It seems that my plan is starting to work.

356
00:15:50,519 --> 00:15:52,399
Ms Yin is very cautious.

357
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:56,320
Her words show both filial piety and hidden sharpness.

358
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:58,480
She's clearly on guard against the young master.

359
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,360
And the young master

360
00:16:00,639 --> 00:16:03,000
is no longer as attentive as before,

361
00:16:03,399 --> 00:16:06,240
but has shown a bit of distance and caution.

362
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:11,440
The more composed and proper Yin Xinyue is,

363
00:16:11,759 --> 00:16:13,759
the more deliberate she seems.

364
00:16:14,399 --> 00:16:14,919
Besides,

365
00:16:15,399 --> 00:16:16,519
my stepson

366
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,120
is shrewd and calculating,

367
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:20,759
never easily showing his preferences.

368
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,679
His coldness today

369
00:16:23,519 --> 00:16:27,519
seems not to have lost affection for Yin,

370
00:16:28,039 --> 00:16:28,840
but rather

371
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,879
testing the waters.

372
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,759
Do you think

373
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:36,039
they're putting on a show,

374
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:38,360
one pretending to be virtuous,

375
00:16:38,879 --> 00:16:40,279
the other acting distant,

376
00:16:40,679 --> 00:16:42,679
but actually working together in secret

377
00:16:42,679 --> 00:16:44,200
to gauge your reaction?

378
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:47,039
Could it be as you suspect?

379
00:16:47,559 --> 00:16:51,240
Have they caught on to something?

380
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,559
If they

381
00:16:54,879 --> 00:16:56,440
are truly in cahoots,

382
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,240
Don't jump to conclusions.

383
00:16:58,120 --> 00:17:00,440
Yin Xinyue left the mansion,

384
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:02,399
and Xiao Jingyi married

385
00:17:02,399 --> 00:17:04,240
the daughter of the Liu family

386
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,559
as I arranged.

387
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,079
But they

388
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,759
insisted on investigating.

389
00:17:09,519 --> 00:17:10,359
Then,

390
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:13,359
don't blame me for being ruthless.

391
00:17:13,799 --> 00:17:14,680
You're wise, my lady.

392
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,319
A great leader shouldn't be bothered by trifles.

393
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:19,319
You should be decisive.

394
00:17:19,559 --> 00:17:20,640
Better to kill in error

395
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,440
than to let go.
